To eneable "moodle/course:managefiles" permission check,
uncomment line 18 on dialog.php

And then...
Teachers, usually have permission "moodle/course:managefiles" set "On" for role "editingteacher"
so they can upload files, easily.

To let Students upload images, set the "moodle/course:managefiles" permission
on a:
1. Site level (role "student")
Or...
2. Course / Category Level
Or..
3. Activity Level

with Override permissions on role Student.

:-)